\c 31
\nb
\v 1 Kwathi konke lokho sekuphelile, wonke amaIsrayeli atholakalayo aphuma aya emizini yakoJuda, adiliza izinsika eziyizithombe, agamulela phansi izixuku, aphosela phansi indawo eziphakemeyo lamalathi, akukhupha kuye wonke uJuda loBhenjamini lakoEfrayimi loManase, aze aqeda. Bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebebuyela, ngulowo lalowo emfuyweni yakhe, emizini yabo\x + 2 Kho. 18.4.\x*.
\s UHezekhiya wondla abapristi lamaLevi
\p
\v 2 UHezekhiya wasemisa izigaba zabapristi lamaLevi ngokwezigaba zabo, ngulowo lalowo ngokomsebenzi wakhe\x + 1 Lan. 23.6. 24.1.\x*, abapristi lamaLevi emnikelweni wokutshiswa leminikelweni yokuthula, ukukhonza lokubonga lokudumisa emasangweni ezinkamba zeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 1 Lan. 23.30,31.\x*.
\v 3 Lesabelo senkosi esivela emfuyweni yayo seminikelo yokutshiswa, seminikelo yokutshiswa yekuseni leyantambama\x + Nani 28.3-8.\x*, leminikelo yokutshiswa yamasabatha\x + Nani 28.9,10.\x*, leyekuthwaseni kwezinyanga\x + Nani 28.11-15.\x*, leyemikhosi emisiweyo, njengokubhaliweyo emlayweni kaJehova\x + Nani 28.16-29,40. Nani 29.39.\x*.
\v 4 Wasesithi ebantwini, kubahlali beJerusalema, banike isabelo sabapristi lamaLevi\x + Nani 18.8-24. Neh. 13.10.\x*, ukuze baqiniswe\x + 35.2.\x* emlayweni weN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Ezra 7.10.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Lekusatshalalisweni kwelizwi abantwana bakoIsrayeli bengeza izithelo zokuqala zamabele, iwayini elitsha, lamafutha, loluju, lakuzo zonke izithelo zensimu; lokwetshumi kwakho konke bakuletha ngobunengi\x + Neh. 13.12.\x*.
\v 6 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli loJuda ababehlala emizini yakoJuda labo basebeletha okwetshumi kwenkomo lokwezimvu lokwetshumi kwezinto ezingcwele ezazehlukaniselwe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wabo, babeka izinqumbinqumbi\x + Levi 27.30. Dute. 14.28.\x*.
\v 7 Ngenyanga yesithathu baqalisa ukubeka isisekelo sezinqumbi, langenyanga yesikhombisa baqeda.
\v 8 UHezekhiya leziphathamandla sebefika bebona izinqumbi, bayibusisa iN\nd kosi\nd* labantu bayo uIsrayeli.
\v 9 UHezekhiya wasebuza abapristi lamaLevi ngalezinqumbi.
\v 10 UAzariya umpristi oyinhloko\x + 1 Lan. 6.13.\x* yendlu kaZadoki\x + 1 Lan. 6.8.\x* wakhuluma laye wathi: Kusukela ekuqaleni kokulethwa kweminikelo endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, kwakulokokudla lokokusutha lokokutshiya okunenginengi; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ibabusisile abantu bayo kuze kusale lokhu okunengi\x + Mal. 3.10.\x*.
\p
\v 11 UHezekhiya wasesithi kulungiswe amakamelo endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*; basebewalungisa.
\v 12 Basebengenisa iminikelo lezingxenye zetshumi\x + 31.14. Neh. 10.39.\x* lezinto ezingcwelisiweyo ngobuqotho\x + 1 Kho. 15.15.\x*. Laphezu kwalokhu uKonaniya umLevi wayeyinduna\x + 35.9. Neh. 13.13.\x*, loShimeyi umfowabo engowesibili\x + 29.12,14.\x*.
\v 13 LoJehiyeli loAzaziya loNahathi loAsaheli loJerimothi loJozabadi loEliyeli loIsimakhiya\x + 29.12,14.\x* loMahathi loBhenaya babengababonisi ngaphansi kwesandla sikaKonaniya\x + 29.12,14.\x* loShimeyi umfowabo\x + 29.12,14.\x*, ngomlayo kaHezekhiya inkosi loAzariya umbusi wendlu kaNkulunkulu\x + 31.10. 29.12.\x*.
\v 14 Njalo uKore indodana kaImna umLevi, umgcini wesango ngasempumalanga, wayephezu kweminikelo yesihle kaNkulunkulu ukupha iminikelo yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 31.14. Neh. 10.39.\x* lezinto ezingcwelengcwele\x + Eks. 40.10.\x*.
\v 15 Langasesandleni sakhe kwakuloEdeni, loMiniyamini, loJeshuwa\x + 29.12,14.\x*, loShemaya, uAmariya, loShekaniya\x + 29.12,14.\x* emizini yabapristi ukupha abafowabo ngokuthembeka ezigabeni zabo, njengakwabakhulu kwaba njalo kwabancane\x + Josh. 21.9-19.\x*.
\v 16 Ngaphandle kwababalwe ngezizukulwana zabesilisa, kusukela koleminyaka emithathu kusiya phezulu, wonke ongena endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, ngomsebenzi wosuku ngosuku lwawo, enkonzweni yabo, kumfanelo zabo, ngezigaba zabo\x + 1 Kho. 8.59. 2 Kho. 25.30. 1 Lan. 16.37. Ezra 3.4. Neh. 11.23. 12.47. Jer. 52.34. Eks. 5.13.\x*.
\v 17 Lalabo ababalwa ngezizukulwana zabapristi ngendlu yaboyise, lamaLevi, kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amabili kusiya phezulu, kumfanelo zabo, ngezigaba zabo\x + 1 Lan. 23.24.\x*.
\v 18 Lekubalweni ngezizukulwana, labo bonke abancinyane babo, omkabo, lamadodana abo, lamadodakazi abo, ebandleni lonke, ngoba ekuthembekeni kwabo bazingcwelisa \add ngo\add*bungcwele.
\v 19 Lemadodaneni kaAroni, abapristi, emasimini amadlelo emizi yabo, kuwo wonke umuzi ngomuzi\x + Levi 25.34.\x*, amadoda ayebizwe ngamabizo, ukunika izabelo kubo bonke abesilisa phakathi kwabapristi, labo bonke ababalwe ngezizukulwana phakathi kwamaLevi\x + 31.12-15. 28.15. Nani 1.17.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Wasesenza njalo uHezekhiya kuJuda wonke; wenza okuhle lokulungileyo lokuqotho phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe.
\v 21 Emsebenzini wonke-ke awuqalisayo enkonzweni yendlu kaNkulunkulu, lemlayweni lemthethweni, ukudinga uNkulunkulu wakhe, wakwenza ngenhliziyo yakhe yonke, waphumelela\x + 2 Kho. 18.3. 20.3.\x*.